  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2593440/extras/8cc251680a8fa157c21c039633c97c44.poster.avif?t=1727344852\" width=520 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2593440/extras/8cc251680a8fa157c21c039633c97c44.webm?t=1727344852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2593440/extras/8cc251680a8fa157c21c039633c97c44.mp4?t=1727344852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Immerse yourself in a colorful journey through universes that does not forgive any mistakes. Jump well in the ball parkour game, where falling can cost you everything!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2593440/extras/59d7c946e9369eaae60c3103578e19db.poster.avif?t=1727344852\" width=520 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2593440/extras/59d7c946e9369eaae60c3103578e19db.webm?t=1727344852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2593440/extras/59d7c946e9369eaae60c3103578e19db.mp4?t=1727344852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In Balling UP you will have to face many arcade challenges, where you not only have to jump correctly, but also keep the ball on sloping, uneven surfaces.<br><br>As long as you touch any surfaces, you can make infinite jumps. Climb the skyscrapers, discover shortcuts and don't let the ball fall!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2593440/extras/deb85665a3f76549e03123fb71a11eb2.poster.avif?t=1727344852\" width=520 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2593440/extras/deb85665a3f76549e03123fb71a11eb2.webm?t=1727344852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2593440/extras/deb85665a3f76549e03123fb71a11eb2.mp4?t=1727344852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
